                          <p style="height:30px;color:white;background-color:#0066CC;border:1px;">This page has been archived and commenting is disabled.</p>                        <h1 class="title">Bitcoin: Revolutionary Game-Changer Or Trojan Horse?</h1>
            <div class="tabs"></div>
            <div class="node">
  <div class="picture">
  <a href="/users/george-washington" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-7813.jpg" alt="George Washington&#039;s picture" title="George Washington&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>

  
  <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/users/george-washington">George Washington</a> on  02/05/2014 01:16 -0400</span><br /><br /><span class="taxonomy"></span><br /><br />

      <div class="clear-block clear"></div>
    <div class="js-links">
      <!-- Place this tag where you want the +1 button to render -->
      <div class="js-l1" style="width: 100px;">
        <iframe allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets/tweet_button.html?url=http://www.zerohedge.com/contributed/2014-02-05/bitcoin-revolutionary-game-changer-or-trojan-horse" style="width:100px; height:20px;"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="js-l1" style="margin-right:10px;">
        <div id="fb-root"></div>
        <script src="http://connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js#appId=231521786893886&amp;xfbml=1"></script>
        <fb:like href="" send="ttrue" layout="button_count" width="150" show_faces="false" font=""></fb:like>
      </div>
      <div class="js-l1" style="margin-right:10px;">
        <script src="//platform.linkedin.com/in.js" type="text/javascript"> lang: en_U </script>
        <script type="IN/Share" data-counter="right"></script>
